.TH DFBG 1 "12 Nov 2002" "Version @DIRECTFB_VERSION@" "DirectFB Manual Pages"

.SH NAME
dfbg \- DirectFB background configuration tool

.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdfbg\fP [\fIoptions\fP] <\fIimagefile\fP>

.SH DESCRIPTION
\fBdfbg\fP is a small utility to configure the background of the DirectFB
desktop. It loads the specified image and sets it as background image.
\fBdfbg\f requires DirectFB with the multi-application core enabled.

.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B -c, --color
Tile the background with the image instead of scaling it to fit the
screen size.

.TP
.B -t, --tile
Tile the background with the image instead of scaling it to fit the
screen size.

.TP
.B -v, --version
Output version information.

.TP
.B -h, --help
Print brief help and exit.

.SH OTHER INFO
The canonical place to find informations about DirectFB is at
http://www.directfb.org/.
